creator: Armongate
descriptionHtml:
Armon is the next generation cloud-based access control system that allows you to easily control all the entrances and exits in your workplace or on your site from a single center. With Armon application, you can manage your access control system from everywhere, report access logs easily, change authorizations, open your doors remotely.

Some of the features that differentiate the Armon Access Control Systems from others are;

• With the option of using in the cloud, provides controlling and monitoring the buildings and offices that are in different locations from a single center.

• Only one installation is sufficient because it is managed from a single center.

• Modern and simple interface makes many operations easy.

• It can be controlled from the computer and smartphones.

• With its advanced technology works with many different readers, sensors, door lock models.

• You can perform many operations through the REST API, or even create your own interface.

While all transactions can be done locally in existing access control systems, all information is securely stored in the Armon servers with cloud infrastructure. You can view access logs with details and change authority changes when you have access to your Internet access.
descriptionShort: You can manage your access control system from anywhere
